---
title: Sesame-Crusted Chicken with Garlic-Ginger Rice
description: The only thing better than a golden crust on tender chicken breast? Adding crunchy, flavoursome sesame seeds to the coating, giving you an Asian-inspired schnitzel that goes wonderfully with fragrant garlic-ginger rice and an easy veggie stir-fry. Enjoy the taste sensation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sesame-crusted-chicken-ee75bdb7.jpg
